{"tid":1781994,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"默克爾不禁用華為惹反彈 德國議員群起背叛","createTime":"2019-12-13T14:36:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-14T15:08:24.000Z","uid":25468,"like":73,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"9561fb67d8912ad176d9e9074ecad3971d0b5854","tid":1781994,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T14:36:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2515000/2519825/20191213_huawei_v1_1024.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2515000%2F2519825%2F20191213_huawei_v1_1024.png&h=d042db15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中美貿易戰打到5G科技戰，美國嘗試封殺中國5G設備龍頭華為，歐洲成為磨心。德國總理默克爾早前一錘定音，拍板不先發制人封殺華為，現在於德國國內惹起反彈。一批德國執政黨議員在國會挑戰默克爾政策，推動一刀切禁止「信不過」企業參與德國5G網絡建設。<br />\n<br />\n彭博社引述德國國會立法草案文件報道，德國執政聯盟兩黨一批國會議員正草擬立法，規定德國政府將「不可靠」（untrustworthy）5G設備生產商，排除於德國「核心與周邊」網絡。<br />\n<br />\n草案雖未有點名，但顯然針對華為等中國企業。德國情報部門與內政部此曾都曾警告，華為與中國政府有聯繫，會對使用華為設備外國構成國安風險。華為一直否認外國這種指控。<br />\n<br />\n默克爾所屬政黨基民盟早前亦支持規定，德國5G網絡設備供應商必須不受外國政府影響。<br />\n<br />\n德國執政聯盟議員現時所推動立法則更為嚴格，主張連華為參與德國非核心網絡建設也不容許。<br />\n<br />\n西方英語國家中，現時美國、澳洲及新西蘭都全面禁止使用華為5G設備，英國則容許華為供應天線等非核心網絡元件，加拿大未有決定。<br />\n<br />\n因此，歐洲大陸國家現已成為中美華為5G角力一大戰場。法國11月表明，不會跟隨美國封殺華為，但會審查所有設備製造商，確保不會存在任何潛在安全威脅。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2519825/%E3%80%90%E4%B8%AD%E7%BE%8E5G%E8%A7%92%E5%8A%9B%E3%80%91%E9%BB%98%E5%85%8B%E7%88%BE%E4%B8%8D%E7%A6%81%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E6%83%B9%E5%8F%8D%E5%BD%88%20%E5%BE%B7%E5%9C%8B%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E4%B8%80%E5%88%80%E5%88%87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2519825%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%25BE%258E5G%25E8%25A7%2592%25E5%258A%259B%25E3%2580%2591%25E9%25BB%2598%25E5%2585%258B%25E7%2588%25BE%25E4%25B8%258D%25E7%25A6%2581%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%2582%25BA%25E6%2583%25B9%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%25BD%2588%2520%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%2593%25A1%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%25B1%2582%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%2588%2580%25E5%2588%2587&d=ZRuO0gn2PDb4CPS%2BM%2Fpj6vUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=e0099aa6\" target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2519825/%E3%80%90%E4%B8%AD%E7%BE%8E5G%E8%A7%92%E5%8A%9B%E3%80%91%E9%BB%98%E5%85%8B%E7%88%BE%E4%B8%8D%E7%A6%81%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E6%83%B9%E5%8F%8D%E5%BD%88%20%E5%BE%B7%E5%9C%8B%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E4%B8%80%E5%88%80%E5%88%87</a>"},{"pid":"fd27e7010bbd58405ca8acc9e06ef09fffb4d551","tid":1781994,"uid":25468,"like":52,"dislike":0,"score":52,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T14:40:07.000Z","msg":"根本全世界都反支 , 默克爾仲on99 以為可以扮中立"},{"pid":"391755c04db4078919d27ddb0ecce12b8f1989bb","tid":1781994,"uid":25424,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"fd27e7010bbd58405ca8acc9e06ef09fffb4d551","tid":1781994,"uid":25468,"like":52,"dislike":0,"score":52,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T14:40:07.000Z","msg":"根本全世界都反支 , 默克爾仲on99 以為可以扮中立"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T14:41:27.000Z","msg":"共青團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d46a4f436e527b128be164f439603bae04df37ee","tid":1781994,"uid":54303,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"quote":{"pid":"fd27e7010bbd58405ca8acc9e06ef09fffb4d551","tid":1781994,"uid":25468,"like":52,"dislike":0,"score":52,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T14:40:07.000Z","msg":"根本全世界都反支 , 默克爾仲on99 以為可以扮中立"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T14:42:13.000Z","msg":"佢係東德人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68eab56822d724c94824a42c4a6d260dd98418cb","tid":1781994,"uid":1477,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T14:47:58.000Z","msg":"有無手足願意幫手堅持十點鐘鳩叫？ 一齊將呢個行動嘅參與率由0.1% 提升到1%甚至係10%<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1781972\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1781972</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"81e40fd4c0d3d41ee89133fa9347942fab09928a","tid":1781994,"uid":14494,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"fd27e7010bbd58405ca8acc9e06ef09fff